164
00:10:30.990 --> 00:10:32.867
<i>jossa sai abortin.</i>

165
00:10:34.618 --> 00:10:37.747
<i>Valmistuttuani collegesta tulin raskaaksi.</i>

166
00:10:37.830 --> 00:10:41.959
<i>Olin Englannissa. 
